  "texts": [
    "Heart disease prediction has gotten a lot of interest in the medical world.",
    "In the study 14 a hybrid genetic algorithm (GA) and particle swarm optimization (PSO) optimized technique based on RF, named GAPSO-RF, is created and applied to identify the ideal features that can improve heart-disease prediction accuracy.",
    "On the Cleveland dataset, they obtained 95.6% accuracy in heart disease prediction.",
    "Their approach achieves good accuracy however, combining several techniques may increase the difficulty of parameter adjustment and convergence of optimization.",
    "The proposed strategy surpasses state-of-the-art approaches, with a remarkable accuracy of 96.51%."
  ],
